To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private EveningStar _eveningstar;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_eveningstar = EveningStar(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_eveningstar.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "EveningStar Period", _eveningstar.Period);
    Plot("My Indicators", "EveningStar Current", _eveningstar.Current);
}
